  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es liſchu juhß no winna\nWiddus tßeet/ un nodohſchu\nuhß Sweſcheem Rohkâ/ un neſ-\ntchu juhfu Starpâ to Teefn.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Juhß krittifeet zaur Soh-\ninn/ es foḣdifchu juhß Israëta\nRohbeschâs/ un juhß fajuttifeet/\nn es efmu tas KUNGS.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Schis(Pulsfahts) jums\nar Pohdu ne buhß/ nedß juhß\nar Galtu buhſeet winna Wid-\nu/ Israëta Rohbeschâs gribbu\ns juhß foḣdiht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un juhß fajuttifeet/ ka es\nas KUNGS eſmu. Tapehz\na juhß mannôß Likkumôß ne et-\nt staigajſchi/ nedß mannas Tee-\nas darrijuſchi/ bet pehz to Pa-\nanu Teefahm/ kas apkartjums\nr/ turreifscheeß.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas notikahß/ kad es\nuddinaju/ tad nomirre Platti-\ns Benaja Dehls. Tad krittu\nus fawu Waign/ un brehzn ar\npru Balsi/ un fazziju: Ak\nungs KUNGS! gribbi tu\neem Israëta Atlikkufcheem wiſ-\nt Gallu darriht?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad notifte ta KUNGA\nBahrdß us man/ kas fazzija:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu Zilweka Behrns/ tee\nr tawi Brahti/ tawi Brahti/\nwi Raddi/ un wiſß Israëta\nams/ wiſsnotaf irr tee us ko\nJerusalemes Eedsihwotaji\nka: Atkahpeetees tahfu no ta\nnga/ ſcht Semme irr mums\nr Eemantoſchanu dohta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tadeht fakft: Ta fakka\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "tas KUNGS KUNGS: Jepſchu\nes tohß tahfu ſtarp teem Pagah-\nneem efmu iſdsinnis/ un jepſchu\nes tohß Walſtis efmu iſkaiftijs.\nTatſchu es par masu Brihdi\nteem buhſchu par Swehtumu/\ntannis Walſtis/ kur tee irr nah-\nkufchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tadeht fakft: Ta fakka\ntas KUNGS KUNGS: Tee-\nfcham/ es fapulzinaſchu juhß no\ntahm Tautahm / un falaffischu\njuhß no tahm Walſtim / furp\njuhß eſtat iſkaifti / un es doh-\nschu juhß to Israëta Gemmi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee nahkß us turren/\nun nemß wiffas winnas Apgah-\nnischanas / un wiffas winnas\nNegantibas no winnaß nohſt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un es dohſchu teem wee-\nnadu Sirdi / un weenu jaunu\nGarru juhfu Widdu/ un atnem-\nſchu to akminainu Sirdi no win-\nnu Meefahm / un dohſchu teem\nweenu meefgnu Sirdi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ka tee mannôß Likkumôß\nstaiga/ un mannas Teefas far-\nga/ un tahß darra/ un tee buhß\nman par Landim / un es buhſchu\nteem par Deewu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet teem / kurreu Sirde\npehz to Prahtu ſawo Apgahni-\nſchano un Negantibo dsennahß/\nmettiſchu es winno Zeftu us\nwinno Galwu/ fakka tas KUNGS\nKUNGS.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad pazehle tee Kernbim\nfawus Spahrnus/ un tee Skrit-\nteti fahnis winneem/ un ta Goh-\ndiba\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
